author: rhuijben
msg: Following up on r33539, perform some code cleanup in gen_win.py.
* build/generator/gen_win.py
(GeneratorBase._find_swig), (GeneratorBase._find_neon),
(GeneratorBase._find_apr), (GeneratorBase._find_apr_util),
(GeneratorBase._find_sqlite):
Don't compile regexes only used once, and use map() to remove doing
the same conversion three times.
Suggested by: gstein

author: julianfoad
msg: Fix a bug in tree conflict detection whereby "svn update" would fail (if run
from a current working directory in which the file was being added) or behave
wrongly on a file add-with-history.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/update_editor.c
(add_file_with_history): Pass the victim path, not the parent path, to
check_tree_conflict().

author: rhuijben
msg: * tools/buildbot/slaves/win32-xp-VS2005/svnbuild.bat:
Removed manual building of javahl-java and javahl-javah as
__JAVAHL__ would build them before anything else.
